  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1641770/extras/f63ea03131f3334de9f53581fc57efe9.poster.avif?t=1756891383\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1641770/extras/f63ea03131f3334de9f53581fc57efe9.webm?t=1756891383\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1641770/extras/f63ea03131f3334de9f53581fc57efe9.mp4?t=1756891383\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>A thrilling 2D platformer where the chase is on—and the nuts must flow!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After saving the world from aliens, our squirrel hero is ready to relax—until a <i>very</i> angry bear steals his precious nuts and bolts into the wilderness! Chase the thief across <strong>four vibrant 2D worlds</strong>, each with unique obstacles, enemies, and challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump, push boxes and run through <strong>action-packed 2D levels</strong>, outsmart the bear’s crafty allies, and recover every last nut. Can you catch the bear and teach him a lesson?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 Unique  Worlds</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenging 2D Platforming</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Crafty Enemies with Unique Skills</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1641770/extras/f63ea03131f3334de9f53581fc57efe9.poster.avif?t=1756891383\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1641770/extras/f63ea03131f3334de9f53581fc57efe9.webm?t=1756891383\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1641770/extras/f63ea03131f3334de9f53581fc57efe9.mp4?t=1756891383\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>A thrilling 2D platformer where the chase is on—and the nuts must flow!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After saving the world from aliens, our squirrel hero is ready to relax—until a <i>very</i> angry bear steals his precious nuts and bolts into the wilderness! Chase the thief across <strong>four vibrant 2D worlds</strong>, each with unique obstacles, enemies, and challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump, push boxes and run through <strong>action-packed 2D levels</strong>, outsmart the bear’s crafty allies, and recover every last nut. Can you catch the bear and teach him a lesson?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 Unique  Worlds</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenging 2D Platforming</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Crafty Enemies with Unique Skills</p></li></ul>",
